definition: not yet/did not/have not/not/8th earthly branch: 1-3 p.m., 6th solar month (7th July-6th August), year of the Sheep/ancient Chinese compass point: 210°

pinyin: guang3 bo1 he2 wei4 zhi1 fu2 wu4 qi4

definition: erhua variant of 未知數|未知数[wei4 zhi1 shu4]

sentences.english: He was a man whoseorigin was unknown and who disappeared without leaving a trace.
sentences.chinese: 他的身世未知，但消失的时候又不留一丝痕迹。

sentences.english: In areas like this, we are moving into the unknown.
sentences.chinese: 在这方面，我们正在向着未知世界探索。

sentences.english: I want to hide myself in a unknown place just as the ostrich in desert.
sentences.chinese: 我想要掩藏自己在一个未知的地方正驼鸟在沙漠。

sentences.english: All that stress is caused by fear. Fear of the unknown.
sentences.chinese: 所有的压力都来源于畏惧，对未知的恐惧。

sentences.english: We love the thrill of the unknown.
sentences.chinese: 我们喜欢未知带给我们的震撼。

sentences.english: But he is also the entity K. who is the x of this flesh-and-blood equation.
sentences.chinese: 但是他也是实体的K，是这个肉体等式的未知数x。

sentences.english: But as prices rise, the global economy is entering unknown territory.
sentences.chinese: 但是伴随油价上涨，世界经济正进入一个未知领域。

sentences.english: A gold necklace with intricate depictions of animals.
sentences.chinese: 一条刻有未知神兽的金项链。

sentences.english: I just can't resist the temptation to get on and follow to whatever destination.
sentences.chinese: 那种坐上去，前往未知的目的地的诱惑让我不能自已。

sentences.english: Argentina are the unknown package of this World Cup.
sentences.chinese: 阿根廷是这届世界杯上的一个未知数。

sentences.english: The method has good preciseness and less unknown variables and it is convenient to be used in practice.
sentences.chinese: 该方法收敛性较好，未知量少，便于实际应用。

sentences.english: Compare with the determination of the empirical formulas of the unknown compounds were also discussed.
sentences.chinese: 文中还讨论了影响未知化合物元素比例式测定的因素。

sentences.english: There were green waves of yearning for life still unknown.
sentences.chinese: 滚滚涌来的绿浪，渴望着仍所未知的生命。

sentences.english: The author seeks to break the methods he created yesterday and move on towards unexplored territory.
sentences.chinese: 作者在写作方法上力求不断突破，去探索未知的领地。

sentences.english: OBJECTIVE To develop a method for identification and analysis of the unknown toxic herbal medicinal powders: Dysosma pleiantha(Hance) Woodson.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究未知有毒中药粉末六角莲的鉴定与分析方法。

sentences.english: It's still uncertain whether the College Spring Sports will be held this year.
sentences.chinese: 学院今年的春运会是否开还是个未知数。
